      "amount": "1 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat air fryer to 200°C (392°F).",
    "Mix almond flour, garlic powder, turmeric powder, and sesame seeds together.",
    "Fold in raw almonds, sunflower seeds, pumpkin seeds, and chia seeds thoroughly.",
    "Transfer mixture into an airtight container for easy consumption.",
    "Air fry the mixture for 10-15 minutes until golden brown, shaking halfway through.",
    "Allow to cool before serving."
